Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.64,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,My brother, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:14.61,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,My brother, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:18.12,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.79,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:25.24,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've come... I've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:27.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.35,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.17,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina! Your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:40.51,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.89,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You need to realize the \Nimportance of underwear already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:52.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,God's Little Prank
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're not just scraps of—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.00,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:12.17,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're... you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:15.09,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're with a naked girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.44,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1)}#07 Her Homesickness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:17.21,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:23.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Earthlings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Testing... testing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.06,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Image by Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.06,Saku-main,FATHER,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.56,Saku-main,FATHER,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing. There's \Nsomething I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:36.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:41.40,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Image by Kamiigusa Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.40,Saku-main,FATHER,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you have my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:46.64,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Earthlings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.33,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}Image
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.33,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.75,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a question for you. Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.08,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Option 1: Yang Guifei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.46,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Option 2: Cleopatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.59,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Option 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:07.25,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We are Earthlings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.88,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, what's wrong? You sound tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At least answer the phone \Nlike a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough on my plate as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.27,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yuko. She's turned up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.27,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.77,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.75,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't my dear brother come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it's summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.73,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's living with a girl \Nin Tokyo in secret to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's doing lots of \Nunmentionable things with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.76,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,After I told her that, \Nshe insisted on going to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, this was your doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:42.01,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Image by Aoyama Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.01,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how it is, \Nso take care of Yuko for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:48.18,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Image by Akasaka Ryunosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.58,Saku-main,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.00,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to talk to you \Nabout her future plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so ask her about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did she just gloss over \Nthe most important part?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.84,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting Station: Harajuku -> Shinjuku, Yoyogi, Shibuya\NFare Quota: 160 Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to babysit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:05.26,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game!" Pitch\NTrain Train (Temp): Original Puzzle Game\NDownloadable Mobile Phone Content
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The results haven't been announced yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.58,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's my little sister, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.29,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't {\i1}you{\i0} act like this is the \Nscene of an affair, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.36,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's just a classmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just say that she's my sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.09,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.09,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just listen to what I'm saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.43,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata is my owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.94,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.65,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina! You're out of control today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit the brakes, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.61,Saku-main,INSTRUCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,The brakes! The brakes, Kamiigusa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's accelerate instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.83,Saku-main,INSTRUCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! Hit the brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.57,Saku-main,INSTRUCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:00.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanda-kun, they gave me \Ntwo free ice creams at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:10.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun has a lolita complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sister! My real sister, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's just your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I could count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.06,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, Kumakichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.97,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A second woman has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:28.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun has been helping me out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.80,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Helping you with what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.25,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.80,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,things like {\i1}that{\i0} to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot. She just said that to be polite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:49.52,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you in this "Oh! There's\N Women Everywhere" harem dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.99,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come back home to Fukuoka with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There are guys here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can hear us through the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.49,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,"Shut up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.76,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,...he says. If you don't keep quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sew a zipper on your mouth. \NParentheses, heart, end parentheses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.47,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,From: Maid-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.20,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A third woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.16,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait another second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.00,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come home with me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why has our hallway turned into a river?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:28.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The bath just broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It finally stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:42.06,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:46.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'm not living \Nhere just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:50.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living in a dorm because \Nthere's something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.90,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.42,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,When we lived near here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you said you wanted to go to Suimei High...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because it was the \Nclosest school to our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:01.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't have you underestimating me, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There really is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do over summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.69,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do what exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:10.73,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So, you really are doing those unmentionable \Nthings with Mashiro-san and Nanami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.34,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Congratulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.40,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Say that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.41,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.13,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I bet right now she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.05,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,... out making trouble for someone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Ralph the Ripper's heading \Ntowards the suburbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The target is a white sports car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Found him! Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:04.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He counters with eye beams! Blammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.87,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yuko-chan, \Nwhat year are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.34,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,My third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.90,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tall for a third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She is a third year, but she meant \Nher third year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.56,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I see. I should've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:24.87,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.39,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's saying I'm really mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:33.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be happy about the \Nroute this conversation has taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're too optimistic, \Nor too positive... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:43.88,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's so great about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:50.66,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Great about... Great about... \NGreat about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sora—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:58.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, look at you. \NYou've got food on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.63,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some on yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-sama, you're surprisingly \Nassertive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That was a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Getting worked up like that \Njust makes you more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm really not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.69,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm really not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to take a bath and\N head over to Kana-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is actually, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.65,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not... That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to do this \Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.61,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! Mashiro-san,  \Nwhat's up with your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:46.91,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Your skin's so white and smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were flatter than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.52,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Your boobs are surprisingly large,\N and your waistline's a knockout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're a human like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.29,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko, you're a dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.15,Sign,ARROW,0000,0000,0000,,Dwarf
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.17,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:03.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Yuko-chan?! Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.45,Saku-overlap,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-san's making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:06.49,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san's are bigger. \NShe's a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, you're soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:12.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, why are you touching me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:16.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, Aoyama-san's soft, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.97,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, whose naked body \Nare you visualizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! N-Nobody's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:27.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun, don't fantasize about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.02,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:32.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,In this country, the law recognizes \Nour right to free thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't give you the right to fantasize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always so—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.97,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san, you seduced my \Nbrother with that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't do anything of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he has someone\N more amazing closer to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.74,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san, you're plenty big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.98,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only dwarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Yuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.08,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll get bigger \Nonce you start high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Big and bouncy, just like Aoyama-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.64,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. My battle is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.27,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you from the clutches of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.76,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,The Clutches of Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's a TV show, it should be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.52,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough being popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.39,Sign,PLATE,0000,0000,0000,,Student Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:35.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Nancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.06,Sign,TAG,0000,0000,0000,,Nanba Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.06,Saku-main,INSTRUCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling Nancy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No announcement of the \Nscreening results yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, don't you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:59.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that the population density of my \Nroom's been awfully high lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.34,Saku-overlap,NANCY,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is an emergency report from Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.58,Saku-overlap,NANCY,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Carlos, the wanted bank robber,\Nhas been spotted on Route 301.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.47,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:07.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Be the way, Yuko,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you want to talk \Nto me about your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.76,Saku-overlap,NANCY,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you don't hurry, \Nyou'll run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:15.57,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That was just an excuse to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.68,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I actually just came to impose on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.33,Saku-overlap,NANCY,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Take a look at the available jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't need anything \Nhere, go back to Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything to \Ndo besides playing games...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and reading manga day after day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.04,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take me out somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.41,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A date...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.43,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.43,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.43,Saku-thought,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Date!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.25,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:55.47,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more excited, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:57.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:10.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have work today, and I didn't \Nget to go anywhere last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to work on your manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:18.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano said I should experience \Nlots of things this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.54,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Experience?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The ABCs of love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No, plans A, B, and C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That was your "annihilate" plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.22,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.84,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,B!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.30,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,C!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:37.06,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I slept in the same \Nbed as my brother last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:41.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! You've got the wrong idea here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:43.65,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.94,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've slept in Sorata's bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:55.06,Saku-main,KUMAKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.22,Saku-main,KUMAKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:02.13,Saku-main,KUMAKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.24,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.13,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.59,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who complicated things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.38,Saku-main,KUMAKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.19,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I only told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, choosing the exact words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that would cause the most confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:15.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel like I don't \Nhave enough HP to survive today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that you \Nalways seem to enjoy yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:25.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're talking to \NMashiro and Yuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's so fun about this, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should push you around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she get mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.21,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, I can't walk like this. \NBack off a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone's gonna get lost, \Nit's gonna be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuko backs off, I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her, Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.19,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If Mashiro-san backs off, \NI'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't want to get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:24.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My contract's been terminated \Non my phone, so... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.36,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamise
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.38,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunes: 100 Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.87,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What will I get? What will I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.31,Sign,FORTUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.81,Sign,FORTUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Very Good Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that Yuko will become smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.09,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that my pitch will make \Nit through the screening process.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.51,Saku-thought,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I wish my brother would spoil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.46,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish my sister would stop being so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.31,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat baumkuchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.00,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that Kanda-kun's pitch gets approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.71,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.23,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.13,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,With milk tea on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it was good to get \Nout of the house for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd stayed in your room,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've been thinking \Nabout the mail all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you wish you'd become a voice actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was just an accident or...
