Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.12,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.28,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring my phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're not any help at all, Mashiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.38,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I'll never see my brother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
